NK016(ma)009:0: na raka dong sprugs kyi sngon 'gro bla ma'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK016(ma)009:2: rang nyid gnyug ma'i lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka'i 'od kyis reg pas snod bcud mi dmigs par sbyangs /
NK016(ma)009:3: stong pa'i ngang las gnas khang dag pa'i zhing khams yangs shing rgya che bar gyur /
NK016(ma)009:4: mdun gyi nam mkhar seng ge chen po brgyad kyis
NK016(ma)009:5: btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad nyi zla ba'i
NK016(ma)009:6: gdan la / rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma de
NK016(ma)009:7: nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rnam
NK016(ma)009:8: pa can du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od zer
NK016(ma)009:9: gdan la / 'phros / dus gsum gyi bla ma
NK016(ma)009:10: dkon mchog yi dam zhi khro mkha' 'gro chos skyong
NK016(ma)009:11: rnams spyan drangs nas bla ma la bstim /
NK016(ma)009:12: bla ma yab yum sangs rgyas kun 'dus kyi ngo bor bzhugs par mos la /
NK016(ma)009:13: ba spu ldang zhing mchi ma 'khrug pa'i mos gus kyis gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)009:14: bla ma chos kyi sku la gsol ba 'debs /
NK016(ma)009:15: bla ma longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la gsol ba 'debs /
NK016(ma)009:16: bla ma sprul pa'i sku la rgyal ba dgongs brgyud
NK016(ma)009:17: bla ma la rig 'dzin brda brgyud bla ma gang
NK016(ma)009:18: zag snyan brgyud bla ma la dbyer med rdo rje
NK016(ma)009:19: sems dpa' la 'gal rkyen spros pa chod par byin
NK016(ma)009:20: gyis rlobs // mthun rkyen mngon du 'gyur bar byin
NK016(ma)009:21: sems lnga rgyud la skye bar dbang bzhi nyams su
NK016(ma)009:22: longs par ting 'dzin rnam gsum rtogs pa skye bar
NK016(ma)009:23: cir snang lha sku'i 'khor lor 'char bar grags pa
NK016(ma)009:24: brjod bral sngags sgrar 'char bar 'gyu ba rang rig
NK016(ma)009:25: bde ba chen por 'char bar nyams chag rtog sgrib
NK016(ma)009:26: dbyings su dag par srid zhi mnyam pa nyid du
NK016(ma)009:27: rtogs par lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi gnas
NK016(ma)009:28: lugs rtogs par sku lnga ye shes lnga ldan kun
NK016(ma)009:29: bzang rdo rje sems dpa'i go 'phang bdag gzhan sems
NK016(ma)009:30: can thams cad kyis thob par byin gyis rlobs shig
NK016(ma)009:31: gyis rlobs // / ces gsol ba ci mang btab pas /
NK016(ma)009:32: bla ma rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi sbyor
NK016(ma)009:33: mtshams nas byang sems bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pa lus
NK016(ma)009:34: ngag yid gsum la thim pas sgo gsum gyi dri
NK016(ma)009:35: ma dag / bum gsang sher dbang gsum thob pas
NK016(ma)009:36: rdo rje gsum gyi dngos grub thob pa'i rten 'brel
NK016(ma)009:37: ma dag / bsgrigs / bla ma yab yum bde
NK016(ma)009:38: ba'i ngo bor zhu ba rang gi snying gar babs
NK016(ma)009:39: pas sgo gsum phra ba'i sgrib pa dag /
NK016(ma)009:40: gnyis su med pa ye shes rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK016(ma)009:41: tshig dbang rin po che rang 'khrungs su thob pas
NK016(ma)009:42: / ye shes rdo rje'i dngos grub la dbang 'byor
NK016(ma)009:43: bar bsam la dar cig klod de mnyam par gzhag
